ing: 1/4 cup I Can't Believe It's Not Butter!Â® Spread, melted
1 (1- 3/4) pound butternut squash, cut into 1/2-inch cubes
n: Butternut Squash with Apple and Cranberries
a: I Can't Believe its Not Butter!
des: "This hearty butternut squash recipe has all the warmth of fall wrapped into this one seasonally delicious dish!"
ins:
Preheat oven to 425 degrees F.
Combine all ingredients in 1-1/2-quart baking dish. Cover and bake 30 minutes. Remove cover and bake an additional 15 minutes or until squash is tender.
